# Curated channels that are NOT reliably present in the upstream source.
# merge_extra.py injects every entry below into dhanytv.m3u on each update so the
# weekly auto-update (which REPLACES dhanytv.m3u with the fresh source) can never
# silently drop them. cleanup_playlist.py dedupes by (tvg-id, url) keeping the
# first occurrence, so the curated copies here win their group.
#
# dens.tv channels (SCTV/Indosiar/MOJI) are geo-locked to Indonesia: they work on
# an Indonesian connection but return 403 elsewhere. cleanup_playlist.py injects
# the required dens.tv referrer/user-agent headers automatically.

# <============================================== WorldCup 2026 ===========================================================>

#EXTVLCOPT:http-referrer=https://tvri.go.id/
#EXTINF:-1 tvg-id="TVRI.id" tvg-logo="https://tvrinasional.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/cropped-png-small-white.png" group-title="WorldCup 2026",TVRI (Piala Dunia 2026)
https://ott-balancer.tvri.go.id/live/eds/Nasional/hls/Nasional.m3u8

#EXTVLCOPT:http-referrer=https://tvri.go.id/
#EXTINF:-1 tvg-id="TVRI.id" tvg-logo="https://tvrinasional.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/cropped-png-small-white.png" group-title="WorldCup 2026",TVRI Sports (Piala Dunia 2026)
https://ott-balancer.tvri.go.id/live/eds/SportHD/hls/SportHD.m3u8

